Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:10.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is the story of what happened to the girls thereafter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:15.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time, on the final Simoun:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.26,0:24:18.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Their Portrait.
